{"type": "article", "id": 56770, "title": "迪士尼和天猫开启米奇周年合作，Gucci 早春广告大片的主题是诺亚方舟 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-09-26T02:27:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 64, "name": "广告"}, {"id": 111, "name": "迪士尼"}, {"id": 1329, "name": "天猫"}, {"id": 3185, "name": "百事可乐"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 21323, "name": "美图"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 103970, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/201809261001191thMO42qLPafsGwm.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><a href=\"http://it.sohu.com/20180922/n550294550.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>王俊凯成为索尼音频代言人。</strong></a>代言产品是索尼无线运动防水耳机 WF-SP900。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018092609242692JtvRrBg6iMKOCA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p><strong>百事 X Alexander Wang 联名罐里面藏了王大仁的神秘留言。</strong>广告里的 Alexander Wang 复古中略带鬼畜，邀请你拨打 400 668 7760 电话。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=t00279ch4yz\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zjLoOkkksms&amp;t=39s\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gucci 发布 2019 早春广告大片Gucci Gothic</a></strong>，此次借用了《旧约圣经》中诺亚方舟的主题，描绘出打扮时髦的年轻人和动物一起造船的场景。背景音乐是&nbsp;Sonic Boom 的 Big City。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=f0712qgxd52\"></iframe> </figure> </div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926101355Vdz7MElDsHu6hJbX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926101355muR0jXQgSWbfDrix.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926101355awN2lBjtID8JXWOy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926101356fiL5kHUOKpyurVCd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926101356MKGIYH30egAlkxQw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926101356db9tYu78ogMZm6WS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926101357FTip4vVBlEdQ08R5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018092610135765d4U1zopjf0kmL7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926101357Aq7mwFKEfS6Ydotk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926101357VTrbEBhRxU7AZu1X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926101357hmrDstqi02vEydHz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926101358bPVrwqDToyvkhi7A.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926101358x9OS3M2IKk7DAbXn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926101359LTwzZSgcNQrPFUY8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926101400mRDE3LY7Fl0VUHyP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926101401hC4W68jcTPvnbdBY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>为迎接米奇 90 诞生周年，迪士尼和天猫合作了主题活动</strong>。在天猫 APP 上除了限量周边的秒杀，还包括优衣库、五芳斋、美特斯邦威等 12 家门店的 “AR 寻米奇”活动（位置是上海）。打卡满十家店就可能获得迪士尼的门票。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926093553RqsxvNpVuzX4iWm6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/39927.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>美图手机在最新广告里展示了 0 到 100 岁的女性，用时 2 分钟。</strong></a>这个审美似乎和美图过去给人的印象不太一样啊。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=h1429qftx3v\"></iframe> </figure> </div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/cmo-strategy/armour-taps-fashion-vet-cmo/315050/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Under Armour 终于聘请了一个 CMO</strong></a>。此前这位&nbsp;Alessandro de Pestel 在美国时尚品牌 Tommy Hilfiger 担任了 10 年的 CMO。Under Armour 的首席执行官 Kevin Plank 在一份声明中表示，Alessandro 将有助于加强品牌的全球营销和数字实力。</p><p>题图来自 Gucci</p>"}